source.name: NSF Freedom of Information Act Report for October 1, 1999 through September 30, 2000
source.description: This file contains the National Science Foundation's (NSF's) 2000 FOIA Annual Report. The report provides detailed information regarding the number and type of FOIA cases we processed in FY 2000. It also includes data regarding time and costs associated with processing these cases.
